  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the present study was to determine whether teaching Karate techniques training
      leads to reduction in communication deficit of children with autism spectrum disorders.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
  <start_date>May 2011</start_date>
